data.description: Luxury Living just moments from the beach! You'll immediately be drawn to the curb appeal that this home offers. The craftsman style home showcases pillars that line the front patio which overlook the clean, custom landscaping. Upon opening the front door, you are met with a stunning entryway footed with gorgeous wood plank flooring. The foyer provides views into the adjoining office and the family room. With an abundance of upgrades, this beautiful home offers everything on your wish list! French doors open to the home office which is detailed with coffered ceilings, chair rail, and plantation shutters. Elegance meets functionality in this homes kitchen which features stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and pristine white tile backsplash. With ample cabinet and countertop space, you'll also enjoy the practicality of the huge kitchen island. The huge family room boasts custom built-ins and a classic fireplace, perfect for chilly winter evenings. Take note of the incredible Vivint security system that has full monitoring around the home. Walking up the stairs you are welcomed by the Master Bedroom and three generously sized secondary bedrooms all with walk-in closets. For ultimate comfort and accommodation, escape to the Master Bedroom suite. With just the right amount of seclusion, the Master Bedroom features a spa like Master Bathroom offering two separate vanities, a huge soaking tub, a private restroom, and an expansive walk-in closet. Head up to the third floor where you'll find another sprawling bedroom/bonus room with a full bathroom!   If you enjoy spending time outdoors, you will absolutely love the screened in back patio, wired with a fan to keep you cool on Summer evenings. Surrounded with a privacy fence, this backyard also offers an extended decorative patio! This pristine home is conveniently located half way between Jacksonville & Wilmington.
